alert.note: Alert for Del Norte Interior; Northern Humboldt Coast; Northern Humboldt Interior (California) Issued by the National Weather Service

info.headline: Wind Advisory issued January 07 at 2:08AM PST until January 08 at 4:00AM PST by NWS Eureka
info.description: ...WIND ADVISORY NOW IN EFFECT UNTIL 4 AM PST SUNDAY... * WHAT...Southeast winds 25 to 35 mph with gusts up to 60 mph. Highest gusts will be on mountain ridgetops. Gusts to 50 mph on the coastal plain and near coastal valley locations. * WHERE...Del Norte Interior, Northern Humboldt Coast and Northern Humboldt Interior. * WHEN...Until 4 AM PST Sunday. * IMPACTS...Gusty winds could blow around unsecured objects. Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may result.
info.instruction: Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.
